        default ModifierArgument toDirectModifier()

      • toExecDetachableResult

        default TokenInstruction toExecDetachableResult()
        Should return instruction producing same results from same arguments but definitely providing detach-able (not depending on context state) result in r7RR register (if any). Without calling this there is no guarantee that results would be valid for the next instruction. Every instruction using internal context's accumulators for results should override this method and provide means for receiving actually detach-able results.
        Returns:

      • toExecNativeResult

        default TokenInstruction toExecNativeResult()
        Should return instruction producing same results from same arguments but definitely providing native (not depending on context state, not wrapped) result in r7RR register (if any). Without calling this there is no guarantee that results would be valid for the next instruction. Every instruction using internal context's accumulators for results should override this method and provide means for receiving actually native results.
        Returns:
